## Common Mistakes to Avoid

| ❌ Don't | ✅ Do |
|----------|-------|
| Use auto-generated IDs for offline writes | Use UUIDs (client-generated) |
| Store large arrays in documents | Use subcollections |
| Query without indexes | Create composite indexes |
| Forget to unsubscribe listeners | Always cleanup in unmount |
| Trust client timestamps | Use serverTimestamp() |
| Store sensitive data unencrypted | Use security rules + client encryption |

