## Summary

### Firestore = Offline-First + Real-Time

- **Offline persistence** works out of the box
- **UUID-based IDs** enable offline writes
- **Realtime listeners** keep all devices in sync
- **Batch writes** for multi-document operations
- **Security rules** protect data server-side

### When Combined with Clean Architecture

- **Domain layer**: Business logic (pure)
- **Data layer**: Firestore repositories
- **Presentation**: React hooks with listeners

This creates a powerful offline-first, real-time, syncing mobile app! 🚀
